  "text": "<html>\r\n    <head>\r\n    <style>\r\n        .unselectable {\r\n          -webkit-user-select: none;\r\n          -webkit-touch-callout: none;\r\n          -moz-user-select: none;\r\n          -ms-user-select: none;\r\n          user-select: none;\r\n        }\r\n      <\/style>\r\n      <\/head>\r\n\r\n<body class=\"unselectable\">\r\n \r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">BIOLOGY CURRENT AFFAIRS AND NOTATIONS<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Every year&nbsp;<\/span><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">World Environment day<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;is celebrated on&nbsp;<\/span><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">5th June<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;to spread awareness, to encourage people to act, and to protect the environment.<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">World Population day<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;is an annual event, observed on&nbsp;<\/span><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">July 11<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;every year, which seeks to raise awareness of global population issues.<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">September 16&nbsp;<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">was designated by the United Nations General Assembly as the International Day for the Preservation of the&nbsp;<\/span><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Ozone Layer<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Mamu River Forest Reserve is a forest reserve and is located in Anambra State, Nigeria.<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Dracunculiasis is a parasitic infection acquired by drinking water from ponds contaminated by cyclopoid copepods infected with third stage larvae of the parasite Dracunculus medinensis.<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">In Igboland, Guinea worm is a common health problem in many water bodies in Ebonyi state and in Igwenu river basin area of Imo state.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">The Guinea Savanna occupies nearly half of Nigeria and is the broadest vegetational zone in the country. It stretches around the middle of the country in areas where there is between 100-150 centimeters annual rainfall and wet season of between 6 to 8 months.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><a name=\"_Hlk43253182\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">The tropical rainforest is the richest biome in the world, containing more species per square mile than any other forest. A tropical rainforest can have more than 480 tree species per hectare. insect&rsquo;s species are the most abundant in the rainforests.<\/span><\/a><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><a name=\"_Hlk43276691\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">The Rain Forest Stretches from the western boundary of Nigeria southeastwards around lbadan and Benin. Sudan Savanna is in the northern extreme of the country in places like the Sokoto plains of Hausa and up to the Chad Basin.<\/span><\/a><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">UNN PUTME Examples<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">1. In Nigeria, the Guinea savanna belt borders the&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">A. mangrove swamps and the Sahel savanna B. rainforests and the Sudan savanna C. deserts and the Sudan savanna D. rainforests and the desert&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">(B. rainforests and the Sudan savanna, 2017\/2018, no 4)<\/span><\/em><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2. In which of the following biomes is the south western part of Nigeria located?&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">A Tropical woodland B. Desert C. Temperate forest D. Tropical rainforest&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">(D. Tropical rainforest, the Rain Forest Stretches from the western boundary of Nigeria southeastwards around lbadan and Benin, 2018\/2019, no 7)<\/span><\/em><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">3. In Igboland, Guinea worm is a common health problem in<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">A. Ebonyi State only B. Ebonyi and Imo states C. Abia State D. Anambra state<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">(B. In Igboland, Guinea worm is a common health problem in many water bodies in Ebonyi state and in Igwenu river basin area of Imo state<\/span><\/em><a name=\"_Hlk46212679\"><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">, 2012\/2013, no 11)<\/span><\/em><\/a><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">4. Mamu river forest reserve is in<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">A. Kogi State B. Anambra State C. River State D. Sokoto State<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">(B<\/span><\/em><a name=\"_Hlk42758545\"><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">.<\/span><\/em><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><\/strong><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Mamu River Forest Reserve is a forest reserve and is located in Anambra State, Nigeria, 2012\/2013, no 10)<\/span><\/em><\/a><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">5. June 5 each year is associated with<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">A. AIDS day B. Ozone day C. World environment day D. World population day<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">(C. Every year World Environment day is celebrated on 5th June to spread awareness, to encourage people to take action and to protect the environment, 2010\/2011, no 8)<\/span><\/em><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/em><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n  <p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\r\n<\/body>\r\n\r\n<\/html>",
